{"tid":2001322,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日晚餐，煎葱餅","createTime":"2020-05-04T12:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T06:11:16.000Z","uid":318887,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d5c58a9f821b31968394341cc1fefba6ab8b09d7","tid":2001322,"uid":318887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T12:27:27.000Z","msg":"有絲問個葱餅點整<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UipDA6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUipDA6Y.jpg&h=5b91172c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就係一堆麵粉加蛋加水攪勻，唔使太杰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rJXE40f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrJXE40f.jpg&h=1da8e64e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n攪到個糊可以慢速滴落黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3vCmyTy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3vCmyTy.jpg&h=d258fc42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tQ07urR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtQ07urR.jpg&h=be2f5fdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後加大量葱，一匙羹豆瓣醬或者你鍾意嘅調味料，加少量油，攪勻曬佢地，等所有葱都有啲麵糊響面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y8EL0yu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY8EL0yu.jpg&h=25489dcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鑊度熱少少油<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j2Y1yTs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj2Y1yTs.jpg&h=237a6514&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n煎到有微煙即係個底燶緊，要郁下佢，差唔多就返轉佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pdCBnML.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpdCBnML.jpg&h=2683754a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二面煎熟就食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m25OYj2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm25OYj2.jpg&h=8b224d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n通常煎到第二面個鑊都好熱，會好快燶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要搖下個鑊多幾下，或者細火啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n頹食勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75fffee6bdfe2ac215a1498dd3d13ed02d4debf","tid":2001322,"uid":33359,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T12:31:44.000Z","msg":"即係薄撐?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337c2dea45bff79d9041527e9efd10d9ac0a90ca","tid":2001322,"uid":318887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c75fffee6bdfe2ac215a1498dd3d13ed02d4debf","tid":2001322,"uid":33359,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T12:31:44.000Z","msg":"即係薄撐?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T12:33:43.000Z","msg":"係掛，唔知喎，都係睇朋友整過夠頹我都識整"},{"pid":"f6295badb5f0af13a3283ea1d10391b991fc4e15","tid":2001322,"uid":53128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T12:36:36.000Z","msg":"好撚掛住宜蘭三星蔥油餅"},{"pid":"18c2bfb1597106c8d654a4be1cb9e5886f1e03ca","tid":2001322,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6295badb5f0af13a3283ea1d10391b991fc4e15","tid":2001322,"uid":53128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T12:36:36.000Z","msg":"好撚掛住宜蘭三星蔥油餅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T12:39:42.000Z","msg":"蔥油餅同呢隻兩回事黎架啵"},{"pid":"d2eb649e662f4dc0a2f30cd65d2b3a902e834576","tid":2001322,"uid":318887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T12:40:18.000Z","msg":"我都想食葱油餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf1d78cb70f112dee26bcba5b29ef90e958f03e","tid":2001322,"uid":12006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T12:42:39.000Z","msg":"好𠹌正喎"},{"pid":"7154e406dcd228bb7427ce47e0b759e8e814ecf7","tid":2001322,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5c5